Class UltracraftServer

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.craft.util.PollingExecutorService

All Implemented Interfaces:

@NonExtendable public abstract class UltracraftServer extends PollingExecutorService implements Runnable, Shutdownable
The base class for the Ultracraft server.
